watercolor in his journey books,

00:01:10.190 --> 00:01:12.480
Aaron was actually a film designer.

00:01:12.480 --> 00:01:15.880
He did backgrounds, buildings,
and other elements for movies,

00:01:15.880 --> 00:01:19.490
