00:13:54.900 --> 00:14:00.210
after a great celebration,
which ends "Quest."

00:14:00.210 --> 00:14:02.720
I also tell children here --

00:14:02.720 --> 00:14:06.010
The imagination, it may not
seem like it's a real thing.

00:14:06.010 --> 00:14:08.520
It might seem like it's
something we just do for play.

00:14:08.520 --> 00:14:11.870
But actually, the imagination
is real, because when we go out

00:14:11.870 --> 00:14:14.910
and we pretend that
we're a fast runner,

00:14:14.910 --> 00:14:17.510
or we pretend that
we can be an artist,

00:14:17.510 --> 00:14:20.920
or we pretend that we can glide
across the sky on the back

00:14:20.920 --> 00:14:27.370 position:56%
of a Pegasus, a small little part of
that play, it ends up inside of us.

00:14:27.370 --> 00:14:30.540
It does, it really does.

00:14:30.540 --> 00:14:34.930
It ends up inside of us, and
one day it can become real.

00:14:34.930 --> 00:14:36.710
That's how we use our imagination

00:14:36.710 --> 00:14:40.160
to manifest what we might
want to become one day.

00:14:40.160 --> 00:14:43.150
And just as his children might
have painted a rainbow in a land

00:14:43.150 --> 00:14:45.700
